text: H2O is the eleventh studio album by American duo Hall & Oates and was released on 4 October, 1982. It went to number 3 in the United States, Australia and New Zealand, number 7 in Canada, number 8 in Sweden and number 24 in the United Kingdom. ==Track listing== == References == Category:1982 albums Category:Hall & Oates albums Category:RCA Records albums
